notes.author: Poirot
notes.note: Was in Cairo at the time of the crime.

notes.author: Hastings
notes.note: Says he was on a fox hunt when the crime took place.

notes.author: Inspector Japp
notes.note: Says she was with the Duchess in Cairo. Likely story.

notes.author: Hastings
notes.note: Lovely young woman. Couldn't have possibly had anything to do with it.

notes.author: Inspector Japp
notes.note: She saw a shifty character getting off the train around the time the crime was committed.

notes.author: Poirot
notes.note: Sure she spoke to Michel Stamm on the train to Brighton.
